# Semantic Event Routing (optional)
# Configure per-table transition rules for intelligent routing of UPDATE events
# Format: "table1:col1,col2;table2:col3,col4"
# When a monitored column changes value, the event is routed to:
#   - cdc.<table>.update.transition (business logic state change)
#   - cdc.<table>.update.data (regular data update)
# Tables without rules: no suffix, backward compatible behavior
# Example: Monitor "status" and "kyc_level" on users, "state" on orders
# TRANSITION_RULES=users:status,kyc_level;orders:state,payment_status